com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template

Class TemplateComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template.TemplateComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class TemplateComponent
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity class that modeling the data base table TemplateComponent. Contains the queries to this table used to extract information from her. The purpose of this table is to crates relation many-to-many between table Template and table Component. This table saves information for what template from what components is created.
